<HEADLINE>
<P>
PALM LATITUDES: VERBATIM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 From a press release sent by the Kjellberg Studio in New York: 
</P>
<P>
 "Did you know that your favorite shapes and colors are the keys to 
understanding your personality -- even down to finding the fragrance that will 
enhance your lifestyle? Did you know that you can hear fragrances in music and 
see them in certain shapes and colors? 
</P>
<P>
 "Haarmann & Reimer knows it and they've proven it scientifically, with 
research on thousands of women around the world. . . ." 
</P>
<P>
 If all those women are really hearing fragrances, they need Thorazine, not 
perfume. 
</P>
</TEXT>
