</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A volunteer tractor operator who spent long days trying to help contain a 
4,500-acre wildfire was killed when flames exploded through the area where he 
was cutting firebreaks. 
</P>
<P>
 Sydney Bruce Maplesden Jr., 25, was killed Thursday night by a fire that had 
