<P>
 Paul A. Jacobs, former Culver City mayor, was elected president of the Board 
of Directors of the West Los Angeles College Foundation. Jacobs is a candidate 
for the Culver City Municipal Court bench. 
</P>
<P>
 Established in 1973, the foundation provides the school's students with 
support and scholarships. 
</P>
