<HEADLINE>
<P>
BODY OF WOMAN FOUND IN PALMDALE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The body of a woman who was shot to death was found on a isolated Palmdale 
roadside early Saturday morning, a sheriff's spokesman said. 
</P>
<P>
 The unidentified woman was discovered about 4:30 a.m. on Mount Emma Road just 
east of Cheseboro Road near the Angeles National Forest, said Sgt. Ron Spear. 
</P>
<P>
 The investigation is continuing, said Spear. LOS ANGELES COUN 
</P>
