<P>
COLLEGE FOOTBALL / DAILY REPORT; USC; ED HERVEY SITS WITH BAD SHOULDER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By EARL GUSTKEY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Wide receiver Ed Hervey received a deep shoulder bruise in Friday's scrimmage 
and sat out Saturday's two practices. 
</P>
<P>
 Center Robert Loya, who has missed two weeks with a foot injury, ran on it for 
the first time Saturday. EARL GUSTKEY 
</P>
