<P>
CALIFORNIA CORNER; FESTIVALS, FEASTS & FAIRS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By MARY FRANCES SMITH 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 SAN CLEMENTE -- Artisans and growers share the turf at the Village Arts and 
Crafts Fair and Farmers Market, Sept. 4 in the 100 and 200 blocks of Avenida 
del Mar. Fresh produce available 9 a.m.-2 p.m.; arts and crafts for sale, 10 
a.m.-4 p.m. In addition, a storyteller and face painters join the scene. Free. 
(714) 361-0735. 
</P>
