miniatures: The San Jose Fall Doll Show and Sale features all of the above and 
more, 10 a.m.-4 p.m. Sept. 10 at the Santa Clara County Fairgrounds, 344 Tully 
Road. $4, general; $2, children 5-12; free for those under 5. (415) 459-1998. 
GUERNEVILLE -- The Russian River Jazz Festival stages top-notch tunes in an 
