Riviera Park Research and Communications Center, 2030 Alameda Padre Serra. $30 
in advance; $35 at the door. Proceeds benefit the Arthritis Foundation. (805) 
687-1592. 
</P>
<P>
 Call listed phone numbers for directions. MARY FRANCES SMITH 
